_info.comment: have a call to e.g. identity built-in that specifies output size more than input size. Check that only the short amount is available with RETURNDATA.  CALL is with 100000 as gas, address 4 as destination, 0 as value, 0 as in-offset, 16 as in-size, 16 as out-offset, 32 as out-size.  The returndatasize should see 16.
